{"tid":1897133,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"＊見到有多笑柒日本公司劣質文化攪到肺炎會大流行踩鳩日本既PO.. 不如又睇下D積極對應既公司?","createTime":"2020-02-25T14:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:21:09.000Z","uid":58038,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"88e1d7965cf5ad12e71ae877c8824ce21e49ba6b","tid":1897133,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"見到好多PO踩完日本D垃圾公司社畜文化就笑鳩韓國大爆發<br />\n總之就係咁笑鳩其他國家廢, 唔知有心定無意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然日本D公司文化真係眾所周知既鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係想講都有D公司係好積極咁去對抗今次WARS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間公司就係ブシロード, 即係武士道。 算係日本既動漫業黎講既大公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間公司涉獵既範圍都幾廣, 動畫, 漫畫, 歌, 演唱會, 聲優, 卡GAME, 甚至摔角都有份..<br />\n雖然間公司對班FANS好撚柒閪, 間公司亦好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老母ON99<br />\n簡單介紹完間公司, 雖然好撚閪, 但今次既應變速度以我所知真係動畫業黎講既第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對外既, 上星期開始已經幾乎即時取消哂去到3月底前既發售event呀, 演唱會之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連算係動畫界一年一度既盛事AnimeJapan都取消哂所有展位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://bushiroad.com/information/67\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbushiroad.com%2Finformation%2F67&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=4f59c2d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bushiroad.com/information/67</a><br />\n<br />\n對內既就實行左來客禁止同訪問禁止, 唔急既見面亦都禁止左, 間公司大佬都講過話係日本黎講要完全做到home office係有一定難度, 所以都好努力咁導入緊視像通話, skype之類黎應對, 亦都即刻掃左好多部notebook之類比職員去home office用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然家下其實都已經算遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但始終d文化惡習唔係一時三刻即刻洗走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真心都睇得出呢間公司好撚有心去應對今次WARS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋都算動漫業黎講既大公司, 算係為同行立左個榜樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到好多人笑鳩日本人廢反應慢抵死政治冷感, 但想講其實都真係有公司好積極應對, 屌鳩政府無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知D人踩完日本再笑韓國究竟咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc17af78b6f08b9eac6d7fe26baea37aeddb6d2","tid":1897133,"uid":6828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"藍莓清好波"},{"pid":"70ff4e594ad578e2c818cebf057c538be6e2cdf7","tid":1897133,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc17af78b6f08b9eac6d7fe26baea37aeddb6d2","tid":1897133,"uid":6828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"藍莓清好波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:04:03.000Z","msg":"垃圾post唔洗再回由佢沉"},{"pid":"22a02d5ab813d1d8316ef48f5505f99c33ee6223","tid":1897133,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"有d都轉左home office"},{"pid":"5382af4f5de5bafcfc9fe7fdea453140d235dce0","tid":1897133,"uid":58038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"22a02d5ab813d1d8316ef48f5505f99c33ee6223","tid":1897133,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"有d都轉左home office"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:21:09.000Z","msg":"但d踩鳩日韓既po永遠都剩係會講d職場文化幾垃圾又點樣發住燒都返工<br />\n總之就踩到日韓全部都係垃圾咁抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}